text.tspan: Domestic supply of chillies and peppers, 1961 to 2022
Quantity of a commodity available for use within a country after accounting for trade and stock changes. It is
calculated as production plus imports, minus exports, and adjusted for changes in stocks.
Data source: Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations (2024)
Note: FAOSTAT applies a methodological change from the year 2010 onwards.
